quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  14,28,"Did you not see those who exchanged God’s favor with disbelief, and they brought about their people to the house of doom"
  14,29,"Hell, they enter (and burn in) it, and it is bad place to stay"
  14,30,"And they made equals to God in order to misguide (people) from His way. Say: enjoy, for your final return is to the fire"
  14,31,"Say to My servants, those who believed, to perform the mandatory prayer and to spend secretly and openly from what We provided them, before a day comes that there is no trading and no friendship in it"
  14,32,"God is the One who created the skies and the earth and sent down rain from the sky, then He brought out the produce as your provision with it, and He brought the ship under your control (and at your service) so that you sail in the sea by His command, and He brought rivers under your control"
  14,33,"And He brought the sun and the moon, which continuously hold their courses (orbits), under your control (to be of service o you), And He brought the night and the day under your control"
  14,34,"And He gave you from all that you asked Him. And if you count God’s favor, you cannot count it. The human being is certainly wrongdoer and ungrateful"